title: India Seeks to Tax Jane Street’s Profits, Economic Times Says
description: Indian officials recommended denying Jane Street Group LLC’s benefits under a tax treaty with Singapore, the Economic Times newspaper reported, threatening to compound the trading firm’s challenges in the South Asian nation.
